comments: Durant (BKN) firms up in Rozier's (CHA) path and marginal contact occurs as Rozier is moving through the pick.
McDaniels (CHA) firms up in O'Neale's (BKN) path and the contact during the pick is marginal.
Irving (BKN) moves alongside Oubre Jr.'s (CHA) path and maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt.
Rozier's (CHA) hand slides off of Durant's (BKN) front as he is moving over the top of the pick.
McDaniels (CHA) briefly places his hands on Durant (BKN) and Durant raises his own arm into McDaniels, but the contact during the sequence is marginal.
Replay review of the foul called on Rozier (CHA) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Rozier initiates contact to Irving's (BKN) arm that affects his gather and shot attempt.
Plumlee (CHA) shuffles his feet before starting his upward shooting motion.
Durant (BKN) makes contact with Plumlee's (CHA) arm that affects his shot attempt near the rim.
Rozier (CHA) moves alongside Irving's (BKN) path and maintains a legal guarding position while contesting the driving shot attempt.
Replay review of the OOB called on BKN pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Oubre Jr. (CHA) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Durant (BKN) and Oubre Jr. (CHA) come together and marginal contact occurs as both players go for the loose ball.
Plumlee (CHA) and Harris (BKN) mutually engage and disengage during the rebound attempt.
